{"title":"Mac 上 matplotlib 中文乱码问题","uid":"b99ed2ecd38c42cbeac96cac3cc6d8aa","slug":"PlotZh","date":"2022-03-28T09:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-28T09:00:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/PlotZh.json","keywords":["Linux","LaTeX","Blog","Geek"],"cover":"https://img.swz128.top/PlotZh_File/05.png","content":"<h1 id=\"Mac-上-matplotlib-中文乱码问题\"><a href=\"#Mac-上-matplotlib-中文乱码问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Mac 上 matplotlib 中文乱码问题\"></a>Mac 上 matplotlib 中文乱码问题</h1><h2 id=\"解决方案\"><a href=\"#解决方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决方案\"></a>解决方案</h2><ol>\n<li><p>首先查找系统已安装的字体。打开系统应用「字体册」</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>找到满意的字体，这里我们以「苹方」为例，然后点击 <strong>在访达中显示</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/PlotZh_File/02.png\"></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>在这里可以看到该字体文件的名称，例如「苹方」的名称为 <code>PingFang.ttc</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/PlotZh_File/03.png\"></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>修改matplotlib的一个配置文件，文件在 <code>~/.matplotlib/</code> 中，我的名称是 <code>fontlist-v330.json</code> 根据版本不同，可能有变化</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">vim ~&#x2F;.matplotlib&#x2F;fontlist-v330.json</code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>搜索 <code>ttflist</code> 字段</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&#x2F;ttflist</code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>在这个列表中新增：</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-json\" data-language=\"json\"><code class=\"language-json\">&#123;\n   &quot;fname&quot;: &quot;&#x2F;System&#x2F;Library&#x2F;Fonts&#x2F;PingFang.ttc&quot;,\n   &quot;name&quot;: &quot;PingFang&quot;,\n   &quot;style&quot;: &quot;normal&quot;,\n   &quot;variant&quot;: &quot;normal&quot;,\n   &quot;weight&quot;: 400,\n   &quot;stretch&quot;: &quot;normal&quot;,\n   &quot;size&quot;: &quot;scalable&quot;,\n   &quot;__class__&quot;: &quot;FontEntry&quot;\n&#125;,</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/PlotZh_File/04.png\"></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li><p>保存退出 <code>:wq</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>测试</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nplt.rcParams[&quot;font.sans-serif&quot;]&#x3D;[&quot;PingFang&quot;] #设置字体\nplt.rcParams[&quot;axes.unicode_minus&quot;]&#x3D;False #正常显示负号\nyear &#x3D; [2017, 2018, 2019, 2020]\npeople &#x3D; [20, 40, 60, 70]\n#生成图表\nplt.plot(year, people)\nplt.xlabel(&#39;年份&#39;)\nplt.ylabel(&#39;人口&#39;)\nplt.title(&#39;人口增长&#39;)\n#设置纵坐标刻度\nplt.yticks([0, 20, 40, 60, 80])\n#设置填充选项：参数分别对应横坐标，纵坐标，纵坐标填充起始值，填充颜色\nplt.fill_between(year, people, 20, color &#x3D; &#39;green&#39;)\n#显示图表\nplt.show()</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/PlotZh_File/05.png\"></p>\n<p>大功告成！</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\"><a href=\"#参考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考\"></a>参考</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/c855bae924ce\">解决python中matplotlib中文乱码 for Mac</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"版权声明\"><a href=\"#版权声明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"版权声明\"></a>版权声明</h2><ul>\n<li>作者：麟子</li>\n<li>地址：<a href=\"https://swz128.top/post/plotzh\">https://swz128.top/post/plotzh</a></li>\n<li>协议：<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/deed.zh\">CC BY-SA 4.0</a> 欢迎转载，务必注明出处</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"Mac 上 matplotlib 中文乱码问题解决方案 首先查找系统已安装的字体。打开系统应用「字体册」 找到满意的字体，这里我们以「苹方」为例，然后点击 在访达中显示 在这里可以看到该字体文件的名称，例如「苹方」的名称为 PingFang.ttc 修改matplotlib的一个...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"记录","slug":"记录","count":1,"path":"api/categories/记录.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Mac","slug":"Mac","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Mac.json"},{"name":"matplotlib","slug":"matplotlib","count":1,"path":"api/tags/matplotlib.json"},{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":1,"path":"api/tags/python.json"},{"name":"中文","slug":"中文","count":1,"path":"api/tags/中文.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Mac-%E4%B8%8A-ma